#   Yuno
##   Ideas
*  Rust-like inferred lifetimes
*  Automatic/deterministic memory management
*  Inferred static types
*  Under-the-mood automatic mutation of 
cache-friendly data strctures
*  Non-performant operations are made 
explicit
*  As good as possible TypeScript/WASM 
binding integration
* 
